               VALUES ($1, $2, $3)
               RETURNING id as "id!: Uuid",
                         task_group_id as "task_group_id!: Uuid",
                         depends_on_group_id as "depends_on_group_id!: Uuid",
                         created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                         satisfied_at as "satisfied_at: DateTime<Utc>"
